serdev: simplify Makefile

drivers/tty/Makefile has:
	obj-$(CONFIG_SERIAL_DEV_BUS)    += serdev/

so in drivers/tty/serdev/Makefile CONFIG_SERIAL_DEV_BUS is always =y.

